data.description: Cute home located close to downtown Fate!  This property has had recent updates made to it.  Both primary and secondary bathrooms have new vanities, mirrors, hardware and fixtures.  Vinyl planking throughout this split bedroom floor plan.  Kitchen boasts granite countertops with open concept layout.  Decorative lighting and accent walls make this home feel extra warm and cozy!
